System Pages Wireframe (AECS)

Pages:
1. Systems Overview
2. Linear Ceiling System
3. Grid Ceiling System
4. Custom Engineering System
5. Hybrid System

Structure per page:

[Hero Section]
- System Name
- Engineering Definition

[Logic Section]
- How system works
- Engineering constraints

[Application Section]
- Use cases
- Industry fit

[Technical Section]
- Material logic
- Structural behavior

[Execution Section]
- Installation overview
- QA/QC notes

[CTA Section]
- Request Engineering Analysis
